metaResult.description: High Dive is a surrealist image that depicts a man upside-down on his head within a small container of water. The image itself is a play on the saying, “A Big Fish In A Small Pond”. Rather than literal, the image aims to convey the desire of growth within one’s current surroundings that can be constraining. The image is lit from natural light and shot in a way to capture the richness of the subjects skin while achieving deep blacks that retain textural details.
